                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">quelíteno</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>quelíteno</caption><tr><td>qu</td><td>e-</td><td>líte</td><td>=no</td></tr><tr><td>IRR</td><td>1pl</td><td>lower</td><td>=1pl</td></tr><td colspan="4">'We will lower'</td></table></span></span>. 
