                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">cotóbaya</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>cotóbaya</caption><tr><td>cu-</td><td>tóba</td><td>=ya</td></tr><tr><td>PERF</td><td>pull(PERF)</td><td>=1s</td></tr><td colspan="3">'I pulled'</td></table></span></span>. 
                        pretérito, 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">cagóbaya</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>cagóbaya</caption><tr><td>ca-</td><td>góba</td><td>=ya</td></tr><tr><td>IRR</td><td>pull(not-PERF)</td><td>=1s</td></tr><td colspan="3">'I will pull'</td></table></span></span>, 
                        futu<br>ro, plural del presente, 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">tetóbano</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>tetóbano</caption><tr><td>t-</td><td>e-</td><td>tóba</td><td>=no</td></tr><tr><td>HAB</td><td>1pl</td><td>pull(PERF)</td><td>=1pl</td></tr><td colspan="4">'we pull'</td></table></span></span>, 
                        del pretérito. 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">pe-<br>tóbano</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>petóbano</caption><tr><td>p-</td><td>e-</td><td>tóba</td><td>=no</td></tr><tr><td>PERF</td><td>1pl</td><td>pull(PERF)</td><td>=1pl</td></tr><td colspan="4">'we pulled'</td></table></span></span>, 
