                  <div id="arte2.6.4.4">
                     <h4 class="outline-header">2.6.4.4  4. Conjugación</h4>
                     <h4>
                        4. CONJUGACIÓN.</h4>
                     <p><br>¶Los verbos de. 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">To</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>To</caption><tr><td>t-</td><td>o-</td></tr><tr><td>HAB</td></tr><td colspan="2">'[habitual prefix &lt;t-&gt; followed by an &lt;o&gt;, interpreted together by Cordova as a verbal prefix]'</td></table></span></span>. 
                        activos
                        son muchos, pero 
                        co<br>mo todos los que 
                        son meros 
                        activos 
                        son regulares,
                        <br>no hay en ellos 
                        dificultad alguna. 
                        V.g. 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">Totópaya</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>Totópaya</caption><tr><td>t-</td><td>o-</td><td>tópa</td><td>=ya</td></tr><tr><td>HAB</td><td>CAUS</td><td>join(w/CAUS)</td><td>=1s</td></tr><td colspan="4">'I join'</td></table></span></span>,
                        <br>ayuntar o juntar, 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">petópaya</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>petópaya</caption><tr><td>pee-</td><td>tópa</td><td>=ya</td></tr><tr><td>PERF:CAUS</td><td>join(w/CAUS)</td><td>=1s</td></tr><td colspan="3">'I joined'</td></table></span></span>, 
                        pretérito, 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">cotópaya</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>cotópaya</caption><tr><td>c-</td><td>o-</td><td>tópa</td><td>=ya</td></tr><tr><td>IRR</td><td>CAUS</td><td>join(w/CAUS)</td><td>=1s</td></tr><td colspan="4">'I will join'</td></table></span></span>, 
                        fu-<br>turo. Plural del 
                        presente, 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">tetópano</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>tetópano</caption><tr><td>t-</td><td>e-</td><td>tópa</td><td>=no</td></tr><tr><td>HAB</td><td>1pl</td><td>join(w/CAUS)</td><td>=1pl</td></tr><td colspan="4">'We join'</td></table></span></span>, 
                        del pretérito,
                        <br><span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">petópano</mark><span class="content hide inline"><table><caption>petópano</caption><tr><td>p-</td><td>e-</td><td>tópa</td><td>=no</td></tr><tr><td>PERF</td><td>1pl</td><td>join(w/CAUS)</td><td>=1pl</td></tr><td colspan="4">'We joined'</td></table></span></span>, 
                        del futuro, 
                        <span class="popover-markup inline"><mark class="trigger">querópano</mark><span class="content hide inline"></span></span>. 
                        En estos no hay
                        <br>mas que decir, porque de las 
                        demás especies que 
                        de<br>llos 
                        
                           salen diremos en 
                        
                           sus lugares. Ve a los 
                        compul-<br>sivos, 
                        reiterativos, y 
                        intransitivos, y 
                        hallarás toda la
                        <br>materia de todos estos 
                        activos que hemos dicho.                        
                     </p>                     
